---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Technical Guides And Resources">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Technical Guides And Resources</h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-8">
      You have access to a wealth of knowledge to help you optimize your heat treatment processes. Within these guides, you will discover best practices for furnace maintenance, troubleshooting tips, and material science insights. We ensure you stay informed about the latest industry trends so you can achieve superior results with every heat cycle you perform in your workshop.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <article class="border-b pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Maximizing Furnace Life Cycles</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Learn how you can extend the operational life of your heating elements.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read More &rarr;</a>
      </article>
      <article class="border-b pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Safety Protocols For Atmosphere Furnaces</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Essential safety steps you must take when handling controlled gas environments.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read More &rarr;</a>
      </article>
      <article class="border-b pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Choosing The Right Thermocouple</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">You will find a guide to selecting temperature sensors for different ranges.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">Read More &rarr;</a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need More Information?</h2>
      <p>
        If you require specific documentation, feel free to <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 underline">Contact Us</a> or visit our <a href="/why-weigu" class="text-blue-600 underline">Value Proposition</a> to see our expertise in action.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
